Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:17.51,OP,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:23.47,OP,,0,0,0,,This feels so good, different from usual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.52,OP,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.81,OP,,0,0,0,,It feels so good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:38.24,OP,,0,0,0,,I never understand what's going on around me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:43.16,OP,,0,0,0,,Nothing makes sense to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.58,OP,,0,0,0,,Full of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:52.25,OP,,0,0,0,,Feel so moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:02:04.77,OP,,0,0,0,,I danced with you in a desert lit by the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:18.57,OP,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to the rabbit and fly high
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,516)}I'll fly high
