Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:08.38,Default,Mutta,0,0,0,,This week's space photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.14,0:24:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宇宙写真で～す！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.14,0:24:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっげえ！\N
